column1: 57 athletes from 6 states competed at this meet!
Results are official as all 6 lifters tested passed the urinalysis screening performed by Redwood Toxicology - Matt Fox, Matthew Sohmer, Luke Sedar, Kevin Varriale, Phil Gowin, Keith Schneider.
1st - Bald Eagle Area High School Power Team - 19 points (tie-breaker, most 1st places)
2nd - Joe's Gym of Erie, PA - 19 points
Number of lifters in the powerlifting division: 49
* Total column is equal to the sum of the best lifts from the Squat, Bench, and Deadlift.
Number of lifters in the bench division: 9
* Best Lift column is based on the first 3 attempts.
* Attempt 4 is for a record only.
